  "texts": [
    "Based on these findings, it is recommended to carry out research on the effectiveness of Metaverse environments by taking these suggestions into consideration in future studies.",
    "Distance education tools have evolved into an essential prerequisite for a sustainable educational process in situations where face-to-face instruction in the classrooms is disrupted by epidemics or earthquakes.",
    "Therefore, instructional designers have begun to investigate teaching strategies that adopt cutting-edge technologies to improve their teaching.",
    "In this research study, several potential consequences of the adoption of the Metaverse-powered synchronous online flipped learning method are highlighted in light of our findings.",
    "Firstly, the quantitative results showed that synchronous online flipped learning supported by the Metaverse-based teaching environment was superior to conventional synchronous distance learning."
